data.title: Flags of country subdivisions
data.text:
This gallery includes flags used by first-level country subdivisions. most of them are official flags, whereas others are only used de facto, sometimes to indicate a desire for more autonomy or independence.

For extensive galleries of flags of low-level subdivisions, see Category:Gallery pages of flags of country subdivisions.

This page or section is incomplete.
